summary: This mod adds a players own mine, a small little FREE! house, there is also loads of orichalcum down in the mine and some guards, if you wish you may kill them, this is a brilliant starter house and lots of ebony to start a little armoury. this is my first mod I hope you guy\'s Like it, I am making a mod for an Arena I need some names for fighters
descriptionHtml: This mod adds a players own mine, a small little FREE! house, there is also loads of orichalcum down in the mine and some guards, if you wish you may kill them, this is a brilliant starter house and lots of ebony to start a little armoury. this is my first mod I hope you guy\'s Like it, I am making a mod for an Arena I need some names for fighters so send me some names (rude or not!)
